text.section:
The notice shall include the following information:
The name of the administrative body that filed the proposed administrative regulation;
A statement that the administrative body has promulgated an administrative regulation that establishes or increases fees;
A summary of the administrative regulation that includes:
The amount of each fee being established;
The amount of any increases to any fees previously established; and
The necessity for the establishment or increase in the fees;
A statement that a person or entity may contact the administrative body for additional information;
The time, date, and place of the scheduled public hearing;
The deadline for submitting written comments as established in KRS 13A.270(1)(c); and
The name, address, and telephone number of the contact person for the administrative body.
